text.paragraph:
Advise pregnant women of the potential risk to the fetus [
                           see Use in Specific Populations (8.1, 8.3)
                           ]. Advise females of reproductive potential to use highly effective contraception during and after treatment with TEPYLUTE for 6 months after therapy. Advise males of reproductive potential to use effective contraception during and after treatment with TEPYLUTE for 1 year after therapy [
                           see Use in Specific Populations (8.1, 8.3)
                           ].

